---
<section class="testimonials">
  <div class="t-wrap">
    <span class="reveal label">Client Love</span>
    <h2 class="reveal">What my clients <span class="serif">say</span></h2>
    <div class="t-grid stagger">
      <div class="reveal t-card">
        <p>"Our old website was embarrassing. Karan built us something that looks like we spent $20K. Online bookings tripled in the first month."</p>
        <div class="t-author"><div class="t-av">MR</div><div><strong>Maria Rosales</strong><span>Luxe Nail Studio, LA</span></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal t-card">
        <p>"I was paying $300/month for a Squarespace site that loaded in 6 seconds. Now I pay $149 for a site that loads in 0.3 seconds and I'm on page 1 of Google."</p>
        <div class="t-author"><div class="t-av">MC</div><div><strong>Marcus Cole</strong><span>Iron & Blade Barbershop</span></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal t-card">
        <p>"He finished the whole site in 10 days. I was expecting months. The quality is insane — I've sent him 4 referrals already."</p>
        <div class="t-author"><div class="t-av">LC</div><div><strong>Lila Chen</strong><span>Balance Studio, Santa Monica</span></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  .testimonials{padding:100px 24px}.t-wrap{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
  .testimonials h2{font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin:12px 0 48px}
  .t-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px}@media(max-width:900px){.t-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;max-width:480px}}
  .t-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 24px;transition:border-color 0.3s}.t-card:hover{border-color:var(--border-lt)}
  .t-card p{font-size:15px;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:20px;font-style:italic}
  .t-author{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}.t-av{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--pop-glow);border:1px solid rgba(232,115,74,0.2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pop)}
  .t-author strong{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;display:block}.t-author span{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted)}
</style>
